        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="setup" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" value="setup() — runs on Core 1&#xa;Serial 921600 · setupEspNow() · setupPMW() · IMU begin · setupToF() · Kalman tune · smartCalibrate() (2000 samples)&#xa;attach RC ISRs (isr0..isr5, IRAM, CHANGE) · ledcAttach 4 motors&#xa;xTaskCreatePinnedToCore(NavTask→Core 1, prio 2) · xTaskCreatePinnedToCore(TeleTask→Core 0, prio 1)" vertex="1">
