        <mxCell id="loop" parent="core1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="loop()  —  Arduino loopTask (Core 1)&#xa;250 Hz · busy-wait to 4000 µs&#xa;IMU.update() → Kalman → attitude&#xa;Cascaded PID (Roll/Pitch/Yaw)&#xa;Motor Mix → ledcWrite 4 motors" vertex="1">
